{"tid":2098772,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X Apple Music聲量問題","createTime":"2020-07-07T17:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T17:42:29.000Z","uid":324568,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d59030a94ed0a731491f404f6004f9d0054f8ada","tid":2098772,"uid":324568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"用緊iPhone x 出街聽歌會用airpod聽apple music<br />\n但唔知道點解永遠開到最大聲 都聽落好細聲<br />\n其他app都好正常<br />\n然後有時聽聽下歌 一去到IG播d片有聲 就搞到我隻耳仔就黎聾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求問有無人知道點解會咁<br />\n去過apple store佢話幫我唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13619ade1023f13179b1c13ef5863265e9c7414a","tid":2098772,"uid":132952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:38:59.000Z","msg":"有d廣告公司無唔同平台唔同loudness既概念<br />\n次次我睇story去到d廣告一野勁撚大聲 屌佢老母<br />\n係spotify到有得較個volume range<br />\napple music就唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74764a862bbbef3ae68104baa83403069522fbca","tid":2098772,"uid":43613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T20:08:38.000Z","msg":"我之前都係咁<br />\n試下去setting &gt; music<br />\n之後將volume limit 較盡佢"},{"pid":"b9ea5cbde72511599a30e827d0af605df931c70e","tid":2098772,"uid":324568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:42:29.000Z","msg":"好 唔該曬大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}